title: Digitale Bibliothek 5000 Bildpostkarten The Yorck Project TYP03
description:
This is part of the awesome german series Digitale Bibliothek. For more information, see www.digitale-bibliothek.de or www.zeno.org.
Sorry, this exists only in German.
This is just the data directory, in order to use it, download the software at www.digitale-bibliothek.de for free, register with them (also free) and you get the possibility to install all the volumes to disk. Put the folder TYP03 inside this directory and it will work just fine.
